messages.ssml:
<speak>Everyone is at risk to get <sub alias="covid 19">COVID-19</sub>, though not everyone will have the same severity of symptoms.  The CDC has stated that older adults and people of any age who have serious underlying medical conditions may be at higher risk for more serious complications from <sub alias="covid 19">COVID-19</sub>.
</speak>
